channel.title: TestDriven.NET 2.0 RC1
channel.description: Jamie Cansdale has released RC1 of the new version of TestDriven.NET.  For those of you that don't know it TestDriven.NET is an excellent unit test integration plug-in for Visual Studio 2005 and 2003.  Scott Hanselman recently voted it number 11...
